You've been trolling these boards and complaining about the Mods since before I did the job, and that was a *Long* time ago.  The answer always has been exactly the same.  Jaxy has no obligation to provide the kind of board you want.  She's providing the kind of board she wants, and I and many others choose to support it by being here.  If you don't like it go start your own damn board, and we'll see how many folks like your style of &quot;constructive&quot; argument enough to come by and support it.  No, don't worry about us here on Jaxy's boards, we'll get by just fine without you.  Don't let the door smack you on the ass on your way out.<br>
